      "content": "that's a good start for the tone. can you expand on the part about their \"primitive customs\"? maybe add a bit more about how the local culture or social structures are actually a hindrance to their development, and why a stronger, more \"advanced\" European influence is the only way to fix those weaknesses? it would help the character sound more convinced of their inherent superiority.",
